---
import DucLogo from "./DucLogo.astro";
---
    <section class="hero" id="home">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="logo-container">
                <div class="logo-bubbles">
                    <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
                    <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
                </div>
                <DucLogo class="hero-logo" />
            </div>
            <h1>Deutscher Unterwasserclub<span>Essen e.V.</span></h1>
            <p>Entdecke die faszinierende Welt unter Wasser. Freitauchen, Apnoe-Training und mehr im Herzen des Ruhrgebiets.</p>
            <div class="cta-buttons">
                <a href="#kontakt" class="btn btn-primary">Lern uns kennen</a>
                <a href="#angebote" class="btn btn-secondary">Mehr erfahren</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-indicator">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7.41 8.59L12 13.17l4.59-4.58L18 10l-6 6-6-6 1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
        </div>
    </section>
